<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Southern Philippines Institute of Science &amp; Technology Management System</title>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>

  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <!-- ===== HOME ===== -->
  <section class="spist-section" id="home">
    <div class="spist-content reveal">
      <h2 sclass="spist-welcome">Welcome to</h2>
      <h1 class="spist-title">Southern Philippines Institute <br>Institute of Science & Technology</h1>
      <div class="spist-buttons">
        <a href="/login" class="btn-spist btn-login">
          <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Log In
        </a>
        <a href="/signup" class="btn-spist btn-signup">
          <i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i> Sign Up
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== VISION ===== -->
  <section class="content-section section-alt" id="vision">
    
    <div class="section-inner reveal">
      <h2 class="section-title">VISION</h2>
      <div class="section-divider"></div>
      <div class="section-body">
        <p>
          The SPiST Library envisions itself as a dynamic learning hub that empowers
          students, faculty, and researchers with seamless access to knowledge and
          information resources.
        </p>
        <p>
          We are committed to fostering a culture of reading, lifelong learning, and
          academic excellence by providing a well-organized, technology-enabled
          environment that supports the intellectual growth of the entire SPiST community.
        </p>
        <p>
          Through continuous innovation and responsive library services, we strive to be
          an indispensable partner in the educational journey of every learner within the
          Southern Philippines Institute of Science and Technology.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== ABOUT US ===== -->
  <section class="content-section" id="about">
    
    <div class="section-inner reveal">
      <h2 class="section-title">ABOUT US</h2>
      <div class="section-divider"></div>
      <div class="section-body">
        <p>
          The SPiST Library Management System is the official digital platform of the
          Southern Philippines Institute of Science and Technology Library. It is
          designed to streamline borrowing, returning, and managing library resources
          for students, faculty, and staff.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our system offers features such as book search and browsing, real-time
          borrowing records, account management, and automated notifications â€” all
          aimed at making your library experience faster and more convenient.
        </p>
        <p>
          The library is staffed by dedicated librarians and support personnel who are
          always ready to assist you in finding the resources you need for your academic
          and research endeavors.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== CONTACT US ===== -->
